id: REQ-rtl-on-parse-failure
kind: requirement
name: RTL on any parse or backend failure
status: draft
description: On any JSON parse error, backend exception, or map composition failure the planner shall return an RTL command rather than propagating the exception. The system shall never crash or stall due to a VLM failure.
derives_from: NEED-safe-flight
verification_status: not-run
satisfied_by: CMP-planner
verified_by: VER-rtl-on-parse-failure
